name: Security Advisory Board
description: This wallet belongs to a current Decentraland DAO Security Advisory Board (SAB) member. This committee is responsible for overseeing sensible operations of the DAO, and are the only ones with the power to halt operations initiated by the DAO Committee or community members.

name: DAO Committee
description: This wallet belongs to a current Decentraland DAO Committee member. This committee is responsible for executing relevant DAO on-chain transactions.
